data.description: Welcome to your spacious and inviting 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom haven, perfectly nestled in a prime location! This charming home offers a versatile layout with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths conveniently situated downstairs, while a secluded upstairs bedroom and bath provide a private retreat. Step inside to discover the allure of hardwood flooring that gracefully guides you through the home, leading to the heart of the house adorned with elegant granite countertops in the kitchen. Your culinary adventures await in this tastefully appointed space. Breakfast area features built in bar area perfect for wet bar or other purpose. Unwind in the tranquility of the main bathroom's tiled shower or indulge in the luxury of the custom closet within the main bedroom, adding a touch of comfort to your lifestyle. Entertain effortlessly with two dining areas that create the perfect ambiance for gatherings. Step outside to a fenced yard, where a covered patio beckons for al fresco dining or relaxed lounging alongside the stock tank pool, offering a serene oasis. This full-brick home boasts not only comfort but also practicality with sidewalks, a neighborhood park nearby, and the added convenience of being within the coveted Matt Arthur Elementary, Perry Middle, and Veterans High School zone. Enjoy the ease of access to I-75, Robins Air Force Base, and numerous industries, making commuting a breeze. Embrace the convenience of proximity to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment, ensuring that all your lifestyle needs are effortlessly met.  With the added comfort of knowing HVAC system was replaced Dec 2023, this residence offers an ideal blend of style and convenience in a coveted location.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home sweet home!
